<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She's the beauty who won the heart of Matt Agnew on last year's season of The Bachelor. </p>

<p>And on Thursday, Chelsie McLeod revealed the exact workout behind her sensational physique - and it only takes 30 minutes.</p>

