<p>Stunner! On Thursday, former Bachelor star Chelsie McLeod (pictured) revealed the EXACT workout behind her sensational physique and it only takes 30 minutes</p>

<p>The hardcore workout shows that Chelsie favours high-intensity interval training.</p>

